{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Welcome to <i>Herogue</i>! Customize the perfect team and forge your way to victory in this turn-based, roguelike battler!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Game Features</strong>: </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><i><strong>One-of-a-kind mechanics</strong></i>: Each character has their own unique mechanics. Customize the fighting style that's best for you.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><i><strong>Upgrades</strong></i>: Use EXP coins to upgrade characters. Choose from an array of enhancement paths, allowing you to cultivate multiple styles for the same character. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2067270/extras/Gif3_AdobeExpress.gif?t=1738252097\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong><i>Build a Team</i></strong>: Based on your strategy and likes, customize your team whenever you see fit. Who knows how a few tweaks will affect the whole team? </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2067270/extras/Gif1_AdobeExpress.gif?t=1738252097\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong><i>Tons of Statuses &amp; Buffs</i></strong>: With tons of buffs, debuffs, and statuses floating around, they may be the key to victory...or defeat! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2067270/extras/Gif2_AdobeExpress.gif?t=1738252097\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><i><strong>Tag Team Mechanics</strong><